Ranger Help for: study
======================

SYNTAX:      study
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     15
SKILL TYPE:  cartography

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to perform a detailed analysis of their
current area, revealing information about the terrain, exits, hidden
features, and environmental conditions. Study provides more detail
than a standard look, including terrain type, weather effects, and
any notable natural features. The depth of information revealed
depends on the Ranger's skill level and familiarity with the terrain.
